        "title": "meaning     of          life",
        "body": "The meaning of life is a question that has puzzled people for centuries and one that likely has many different answers depending on who you ask. Some people believe that the meaning of life is to achieve happiness and fulfillment, while others believe it is to help others and make a positive impact on the world. Still others believe that the meaning of life is to seek out knowledge and understanding, or to find a connection with a higher power. Ultimately, the meaning             of life      is a   deeply personal question that may have different answers for different people.",
